## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not capture the full spectrum of reasons behind vaccine hesitancy. Additionally, the information is subject to the biases of the sources used. Further research, including surveys and interviews with vaccine-hesitant individuals, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of this issue.